{"tid":977421,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不經不覺連Girl's Day都準備解散","createTime":"2019-01-11T07:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T02:59:36.000Z","uid":74065,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ca1053b5057b31bbad680a8b383b56dd1d2885dc","tid":977421,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HmulocFl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHmulocFl.jpg&h=b7cc8c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年迎來出道10年的Girl's Day經過長時間的討論,決定與DreamTea Entertainment美好的分手。<br />\n最早合約到期的素珍將於今年2月合約到期並決定不再續約。<br />\n惠利,YURA,敏雅的合約也都將要到期。<br />\n惠利將在8月初到期,YURA和敏雅的專屬合約將分別在9月初和9月中旬到期。<br />\n三人都和素珍一樣,決定不再與DreamTea Entertainment續約,各自走自己的路。<br />\n<br />\n唔宣佈解散但離開公司<br />\nAOA都好似今年要搞續約問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d6e38cf400756e74d7c7cc0dc7be3ae3822447","tid":977421,"uid":166785,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"早就冇歌出，又紅左惠利，散好正常"},{"pid":"9bcfdaacc9678b90cca0846039796d95005c4dcc","tid":977421,"uid":119290,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"姄娥同素珍兩條廢柴散咗可以靠咩維生？"},{"pid":"3a2987dc0c039f3d8c1906ad656bfa42ba0fcda0","tid":977421,"uid":3405,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:34:44.000Z","msg":"唔comeback繼續簽都無撚用啦"},{"pid":"f556ea5d4b92f346c09395420ab619d3b21d737c","tid":977421,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"9bcfdaacc9678b90cca0846039796d95005c4dcc","tid":977421,"uid":119290,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"姄娥同素珍兩條廢柴散咗可以靠咩維生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:36:49.000Z","msg":"真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外兩個曝光多佢地好多"},{"pid":"a9f11397e47dd6e983076d410cddb8295ca11221","tid":977421,"uid":181527,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy